

SUM - 

1) If want to know the combined exp of all the students who have joined us from different sources [linkedin se jitne aye un sub ka Total exp kitna]\


SELECT source_of_joining, SUM(years_of_exp) FROM student GROUP BY source_of_joining;

+-------------------+-------------------+
| source_of_joining | SUM(years_of_exp) |
+-------------------+-------------------+
| linkedin          |                11 |
| google            |                24 |
| quora             |                 8 |
| friend            |                15 |
| youtube           |                38 |
+-------------------+-------------------+









-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


AVG - 


1) We want to know the AVG of the students who have joined us using different sources [google, friend, quora & Oth]


SELECT source_of_joining, AVG(years_of_exp) FROM student GROUP BY source_of_joining;

+-------------------+-------------------+
| source_of_joining | AVG(years_of_exp) |
+-------------------+-------------------+
| linkedin          |            5.5000 |
| google            |           12.0000 |
| quora             |            8.0000 |
| friend            |           15.0000 |
| youtube           |           19.0000 |
+-------------------+-------------------+







2) We want to know the AVG of the students who have joined us using different location


SELECT location, AVG(years_of_exp) FROM student GROUP BY location;

+-----------+-------------------+
| location  | AVG(years_of_exp) |
+-----------+-------------------+
| bangalore |            9.0000 |
| chennai   |           10.0000 |
| hyderabad |            5.0000 |
| pune      |           17.6667 |
+-----------+-------------------+







3) We want to know the AVG of the students who have joined us from Different Companies


SELECT student_company, AVG(years_of_exp) FROM student GROUP BY student_company;

+-----------------+-------------------+
| student_company | AVG(years_of_exp) |
+-----------------+-------------------+
| walmart         |            7.0000 |
| datamatics      |           12.0000 |
| flipkart        |            5.0000 |
| microsoft       |           15.0000 |
| tcs             |           18.0000 |
| wipro           |           16.0000 |
+-----------------+-------------------+





